original: Lokrantz, Jonas, distriktsveterinär. Mörtfors, f. 10/3/05 i Eksjö av fält-veter. Sven L. o. Anna Maria Lönndahl. G. 34 m. Ellen Lock. Barn: Jan f. 37, Christina 39, Feter 42, Carl Johan 45. — Stud:ex. 25, veter:ex. 33. Ord. assist :veter. v. Skarab. läns hus-fa :!sällsk. 36-41, distr:veter. i Mörtfors dlstr. sed. 41.
translated: Lokrantz, Jonas, district veterinarian. Born in Mörtfors on March 10, 1905 to field veterinarian Sven L. and Anna Maria Lönndahl. Married in 1934 to Ellen Lock. Children: Jan, born in 1937; Christina, born in 1939; Feter, born in 1942; Carl Johan, born in 1945. Education: graduated in 1925; veterinary degree obtained in 1933. Started as an assistant veterinarian at the Skaraborg County House-Animal Society from 1936 to 1941, then became the district veterinarian in Mörtfors district from 1941 onwards.
